
.TH NANI-CLI 1 "2026" "nani-cli 1.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
nani-cli \- watch anime from the terminal
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B nani-cli
[OPTIONS] [ANIME]
.SH DESCRIPTION
nani-cli is a command-line anime streaming tool compatible with ani-cli.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --history
Show watch history.
.TP
.B --sources
List available sources.
.TP
.B --source SOURCE
Force a specific source.
.TP
.B --random
Play a random anime.
.TP
.B -d, --download
Download episode instead of playing.
.SH FILES
~/.config/nani-cli/config
~/.config/nani-cli/history.json
~/.cache/nani-cli/
.SH VERSION
1.1
